Package: mvh
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2024-08-17
Title: My Virtual Herbarium
Authors@R: c(person("Thais", "Vasconcelos", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                     email = "tvasc@umich.edu"),
              person("James", "Boyko", role = "aut",
                     email = "jboyko@umich.edu"))
Author: Thais Vasconcelos [aut, cre],
  James Boyko [aut]
Maintainer: Thais Vasconcelos <tvasc@umich.edu>
Imports: magick, rgbif, sf
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown
Description: A software that includes a set of functions designed to search and download metadata and openly available images associated with herbarium specimens based on taxon or geographical area. Tools included in the package are described in more detail in Vasconcelos and Boyko (2024) <https://doi.org/10.1101/2024.08.25.609600> 
